name: MySQL5
queryCode:
SELECT
t1.`DOMAINS`,
t31.`PERSONNAME`,
t1.`POSTID`,
t21.`POSTNAME`,
t1.`TEAMID`,
t1.`TEAMMEMBERID`,
t11.`TEAMNAME`,
t31.`USERICON`,
t1.`USERID`,
t31.`USERNAME`
FROM `IBZTEAMMEMBER` t1 
LEFT JOIN `IBZTEAM` t11 ON t1.`TEAMID` = t11.`TEAMID` 
LEFT JOIN `IBZPOST` t21 ON t1.`POSTID` = t21.`POSTID` 
LEFT JOIN `T_IBZEMP` t31 ON t1.`USERID` = t31.`USERID`
